OL,3,CAnalysis of the Spring Statement from
OL,4,CITV News experts
OL,6,FThe Chancellor has delivered her long
OL,7,Fawaited Spring Statement on the UK's
OL,8,Fpublic finances, which included cuts
OL,9,Fto welfare and the news the growth
OL,10,Fforecast for 2025 had been halved by
OL,11,Fthe Office for Budget Responsibility.
OL,13,FHere, ITV News' experts give their
OL,14,Fopinions on Rachel Reeves'
OL,15,Fannouncements.
OL,17,FAnushka Asthana, Deputy Political
OL,18,FEditor, runs through the numbers
