OL,3,CAnalysis of the Spring Statement from
OL,4,CITV News experts
OL,6,FITV News' Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana has highlighted the
OL,8,Fkey numbers from today's statement.
OL,10,FOn growth, the Office for Budget
OL,11,FResponsibility (OBR) had previously
OL,12,Fforecasted 2% growth for 2025. That
OL,13,Fhas now been reduced to 1%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
