OL,6,FOn defence, Rachel Reeves confirmed
OL,7,Fspending will rise to 2.5% of GDP by
OL,8,F2027, as previously announced, to be
OL,9,Fpaid for by a cut to overseas aid
OL,10,Fspending. #2.2 billion extra will be
OL,11,Fgiven to the Ministry for Defence in
OL,12,Fthe next Parliament, which Reeves
OL,13,Fcalled a "down payment" on the
OL,14,FGovernment's target.
