OL,3,CAnalysis of the Spring Statement from
OL,4,CITV News experts
OL,6,FITV News Political Editor Robert
OL,7,FPeston has described the OBR's verdict
OL,8,Fas "considerably less upbeat" than
OL,9,FRachel Reeves was in her statement in
OL,10,Fthe Commons today.
OL,12,FThe watchdog has halved the UK growth
OL,13,Fforecast for 2025 from 2% to 1% - but
OL,14,Fupgraded it for every year after for
OL,15,Fthe rest of this parliament.
OL,17,FProductivity (output per person
OL,18,Fworking) is going to be 1% lower in
OL,19,Fthe course of this Parliament than the
OL,20,FOBR had hoped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
