OL,3,CAnalysis of the Spring Statement from
OL,4,CITV News experts
OL,6,F"That's really bad news because
OL,7,Fproductivity has been flatlining for
OL,8,F15 years, which is one of the reasons
OL,9,Fwhy living standards have been
OL,10,Fflatlining for so long," Robert said.
OL,12,FFrom October to now, Peston says there
OL,13,Fhas been "an extraordinary
OL,14,Fdeterioration in public finances."
OL,16,FHe added: "There is a massively high
OL,17,Frisk that, come the Autumn, taxes are
OL,18,Fgoing to have to come up."
OL,20,FJoel Hills, Economics Editor, warns of
OL,21,Fover-optimism
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
