OL,3,CAnalysis of the Spring Statement from
OL,4,CITV News experts
OL,6,FITV News' Economics Editor Joel Hills
OL,7,Fsays the OBR's revised growth rate
OL,8,F"will be seen as slightly
OL,9,Fcontroversial".
OL,11,FThe OBR has, over the years, "been
OL,12,Fcriticised for being too optimistic a
OL,13,Fforecaster," Hills says.
OL,15,FThere has been a "significant" growth
OL,16,Fdowngrade this year - with the economy
OL,17,Fgrowing half as fast as the OBR
OL,18,Fpredicted just six months ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
