OL,6,FIf the OBR does downgrade that figure
OL,7,Fin next Autumn's Budget, "then another
OL,8,Fhole will emerge in the public
OL,9,Ffinances" that would need to be filled
OL,10,Fby tax rises and spending cuts, Hills
OL,11,Fadds.
OL,13,FIn her statement, Rachel Reeves
OL,14,Fclaimed the OBR believes the average
OL,15,Fhousehold would be #500 better off at
OL,16,Fthe end of the decade than what was
OL,17,Fbeing forecast at the time of the
OL,18,FConservatives' last budget in power.
